# Repo-only example environment for blacknetd@.service.
# Copy into /etc/blackchain/<node_id>/blacknetd.env during rollout.
#
# The hardened template now uses literal absolute paths in directives that
# systemd validates at load time. Keep this file for rollout notes and
# optional future node-local settings.

# Example rollout paths for node1:
# BLACKCHAIN_ROOT=/opt/blackchain/current
# BLACKCHAIN_CONFIG=/etc/blackchain/node1/config.json
# BLACKCHAIN_DATA_DIR=/var/lib/blackchain/node1
